          <title>
            <string language="en">Brian Malow - Live at the Koshland</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Brian Malow - leben Sie beim Koshland</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Brian Malow - vivez chez le Koshland</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Brian Malow - viva no Koshland</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Brian Malow - viva al Koshland</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Θ*Ψρηαν Malow - ζήστε στο Koshland</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Brian Malow - viva en el Koshland</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">MicrobeWorld and the Koshland Science Museum present a video podcast of comedian Brian Malow that includes excerpts from his science comedy act on infectious disease and an interview about the geek mystique of science.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Science and Technology</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Social Sciences</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">MicrobeWorld und das Koshland Wissenschaft Museum 
stellen ein videopodcast des Schauspielers Brian Malow dar, der 
Excerpts von seiner Wissenschaft Komödie Tat auf ansteckender 
Krankheit und von einem Interview über das geek mystique der 
Wissenschaft einschließt.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">MicrobeWorld et le musée de la Science de 
Koshland présentent un podcast visuel du comédien Brian Malow qui 
inclut des extraits de son acte de comédie de la science sur la 
maladie infectieuse et d'une entrevue au sujet du mystique de geek 
de la science.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">MicrobeWorld e o museu da ciência de Koshland 
apresentam um podcast video do comediante Brian Malow que inclui 
excerpts de seu ato do comedy da ciência na doença infectious e de 
uma entrevista sobre o mystique do geek da ciência.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">MicrobeWorld ed il museo di scienza di Koshland 
presentano un video podcast del comedian Brian Malow che include i 
brani dal suo atto della commedia di scienza sulla malattia 
contagiosa e da un'intervista circa il mystique del geek della 
scienza.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">MicrobeWorld και το μουσείο επιστήμης Koshland 
παρουσιάζει έναν τηλεοπτικό podcast του κωμικού Brian 
Malow που περιλαμβάνει τα αποσπάσματα από την πράξη κωμωδίας 
επιστήμης του στη μολυσματική ασθένεια και μια συνέντευξη για το 
geek mystique της επιστήμης.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">MicrobeWorld y el museo de la ciencia de Koshland 
presentan un podcast video del cómico Brian Malow que incluye 
extractos de su acto de la comedia de la ciencia en enfermedad 
infecciosa y de una entrevista sobre el mystique del geek de la 
ciencia.</string>
          </description>
